        "pythonCode": "try:\n  if _input.first().json.status == \"SUCCEEDED\":\n    return {\n      \"res\": _input.all()\n    }  \n  else:\n    return {\n      \"res\": f\"Error: Faild to extract Amazon Data\\n\"\n  }\nexcept AttributeError as Err:\n  return {\n    \"res\": f\"Error: Faild to extract Amazon Data {Err}\"\n  } "
