    {
      "parameters": {
        "language": "python",
        "pythonCode": "image_url = _input.first().json.img\nsource_amazon_url = _input.first().json.url\namazon_product_name = _input.first().json.get('name', '')\n\n# Extract brand name (first 1-3 words before specs/numbers)\nbrand_words = []\nfor word in amazon_product_name.split():\n    if any(char.isdigit() for char in word):  # Stop at numbers\n        break\n    if word.lower() not in ['the', 'a', 'an', 'pack', 'count']:\n        brand_words.append(word)\n    if len(brand_words) >= 3:  # Usually brand is 1-3 words\n        break\n\nbrand_name = ' '.join(brand_words)\n\nprompt = f\"\"\"Execute \"Run an Actor and get dataset in Apify\" tool.\n\nAMAZON PRODUCT: \"{amazon_product_name}\"\nBRAND NAME: \"{brand_name}\"\n\nCRITICAL REQUIREMENT: You MUST find the EXACT BRAND on AliExpress.\n\nYOUR JOB: \n1. Search through ALL Apify results\n2. Find results where productTitle contains \"{brand_name}\"\n3. Return ONLY results with the exact brand name\n4. If NO exact brand match exists, return empty candidates array\n\nMATCHING RULES:\n- productTitle MUST contain \"{brand_name}\" (case-insensitive)\n- Product type must match\n- Generic/different brands are NOT acceptable\n\nOUTPUT (JSON):\n{{\n  \"candidates\": [\n    {{\n      \"productLink\": \"URL\",\n      \"productTitle\": \"exact title\",\n      \"reason\": \"Contains brand '{brand_name}' and matches product type\",\n      \"score\": 0-100\n    }}\n  ]\n}}\n\nCRITICAL: Return ONLY exact brand matches. If brand not found, return empty array.\"\"\"\n\nreturn {\n  \"chatInput\": prompt\n}"
      },
